'''碱性磷酸酶'''（{{lang-en|Alkaline phosphatase}}，简称'''ALP'''或'''ALKP'''） ({{EC number|3.1.3.1}})是一类[[水解酶|水解酶]]，可在[[核苷酸|核苷酸]]、蛋白质、[[生物碱|生物碱]]等分子上去除磷酸基，进行去磷酸化作用，在碱性环境下最为有效，故得名碱性磷酸酶<ref name="Tamas2002">{{cite journal | author = Tamás L, Huttová J, Mistrk I, Kogan G | year = 2002 | title = Eﬀect of Carboxymethyl Chitin-Glucan on the Activity  of Some Hydrolytic Enzymes in Maize Plants | journal = Chem. Pap. | volume = 56 | issue = 5 | pages = 326–329 | url = http://www.chempap.org/papers/565a326.pdf | doi =  | pmid =  | pmc =  | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110725161757/http://www.chempap.org/papers/565a326.pdf | archivedate = 2011-07-25 }}</ref>。

==细菌碱性磷酸酶==
在[[革兰氏阴性菌|革兰氏阴性菌]]中，碱性磷酸酶位于[[细胞膜|细胞膜]]以外的[[周质空间|周质空间]]。因为周质空间相比细胞内部受环境变化的影响更大，故细菌碱性磷酸酶更不易失活、[[变性_(生物化学)|变性]]和[[蛋白酶解|降解]]，能保持较高活性。至于碱性磷酸酶为何分布于此目前还未完全清楚，一个简单的说法是碱性磷酸酶在此切割出游离的磷酸以供吸收。支持这一观点的证据是碱性磷酸酶通常在细菌面临磷酸不足时合成<ref name="pmid13666805">{{cite journal | author = Horiuchi T, Horiuchi S, Mizuno D | title = A possible negative feedback phenomenon controlling formation of alkaline phosphomonoesterase in Escherichia coli | journal = Nature | volume = 183 | issue = 4674 | pages = 1529–30 |date=May 1959 | pmid = 13666805 | doi = 10.1038/1831529b0 }}</ref>。然而，也有其他的可能性存在，比如磷酸基团的存在通常会阻碍生物大分子透过细胞膜，而去磷酸化作用可能有助于细菌对环境中物质的吸收<ref name="pmid17793769">{{cite journal | author = Ammerman JW, Azam F | title = Bacterial 5-nucleotidase in aquatic ecosystems: a novel mechanism of phosphorus regeneration | journal = Science | volume = 227 | issue = 4692 | pages = 1338–40 |date=March 1985 | pmid = 17793769 | doi = 10.1126/science.227.4692.1338  }}</ref>。

[[大肠杆菌|大肠杆菌]]碱性磷酸酶的最适pH为8.0<ref name="pmid13826559">{{cite journal | author = Garen A, Levinthal C | title = A fine-structure genetic and chemical study of the enzyme alkaline phosphatase of E. coli. I. Purification and characterization of alkaline phosphatase | journal = Biochim. Biophys. Acta | volume = 38 | issue = | pages = 470–83 |date=March 1960 | pmid = 13826559 | doi = 10.1016/0006-3002(60)91282-8| url =  }}</ref>，而[[家牛|家牛]]的最适pH偏高一点，达8.5<ref name="pmid3003174">{{cite journal | author = Harada M, Udagawa N, Fukasawa K, Hiraoka BY, Mogi M | title = Inorganic pyrophosphatase activity of purified bovine pulp alkaline phosphatase at physiological pH | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-dental-research_1986-02_65_2/page/125 | journal = J. Dent. Res. | volume = 65 | issue = 2 | pages = 125–7 |date=February 1986 | pmid = 3003174 | doi = 10.1177/00220345860650020601 }}</ref>。

==人类碱性磷酸酶==
===生理机能===
在人体中，碱性磷酸酶几乎存在于全身所有的组织，特别集中于[[肝臟|肝臟]]、[[膽管|膽管]]、[[腎|腎]]、[[骨骼|骨骼]]和[[胎盤|胎盤]]。

在人类和其它[[哺乳动物|哺乳动物]]基因组中包含以下三种碱性磷酸酶的[[同工酶|同工酶]]：
*{{le|ALPI|ALPI}} —— 肠道（分子量为150 MDa）
*{{le|ALPL|ALPL}} —— 不具有组织特异性（肝、骨骼、腎）
*{{le|胎盘碱性磷酸酶|Placental alkaline phosphatase|ALPP}} —— 胎盘
===用于诊断===
正常情况下成年人体内的ALP水平为20到140[[国际单位|IU]]/L<ref name="Ref_">{{cite web |url=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/MEDLINEPLUS/ency/article/003497.htm |title=MedlinePlus Medical Encyclopedia: ALP isoenzyme test |work= |accessdate= |archive-date=2010-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100616061127/http://www.nlm.nih.gov/medlineplus/ency/article/003497.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，儿童和孕妇的水平会更高一些。
