==在科研中的应用==
碱性磷酸酶在实验室中最常见的应用就是除去DNA 5'端的磷酸基，防止载体发生自连环化<ref name="pmid6246368">{{cite journal | author = Maxam AM, Gilbert W | title = Sequencing end-labeled DNA with base-specific chemical cleavages | journal = Meth. Enzymol. | volume = 65 | issue = 1 | pages = 499–560 | year = 1980 | pmid = 6246368 | doi = 10.1016/S0076-6879(80)65059-9 | series = Methods in Enzymology | isbn = 978-0-12-181965-1 }}</ref>。

